{"tid":2477962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"封殺公司查冊　財庫局稱起底增急需禁查　私隱署:個案去年實跌82%","createTime":"2021-04-06T16:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T16:35:04.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d14a52871661ba90164a9c62e08537887c7b1adc","tid":2477962,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/封殺公司查冊-財庫局聲稱-起底-增急需禁查-避答詳情-私隱署數字顯示去年實跌八成/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%9F%A5%E5%86%8A-%E8%B2%A1%E5%BA%AB%E5%B1%80%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%A2%9E%E6%80%A5%E9%9C%80%E7%A6%81%E6%9F%A5-%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94%E8%A9%B3%E6%83%85-%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E7%BD%B2%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%A6%E8%B7%8C%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=a0a73b91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%9F%A5%E5%86%8A-%E8%B2%A1%E5%BA%AB%E5%B1%80%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%A2%9E%E6%80%A5%E9%9C%80%E7%A6%81%E6%9F%A5-%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94%E8%A9%B3%E6%83%85-%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E7%BD%B2%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%A6%E8%B7%8C%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%2F&h=8cf6350b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/封殺公司查冊-財庫局聲稱-起底-增急需禁查-避答詳情-私隱署數字顯示去年實跌八成/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府本周突然公布收緊公司查冊，財庫局指法例條文早於 2012 年通過，至今未實施，聲稱因近年「起底」個案增加，有「急切需要」落實。<br />\n<br />\n不過按私隱公署數字，涉及地址及身份證號碼的「起底」個案去年大跌 82%。財庫局回覆《立場》時，避答掌握多少宗與公司查冊相關的「起底」個案，亦無回答會否重新諮詢，僅稱將展開立法程序，「各持分者可繼續表達意見」。"}]}